{
  "stem": "5837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really-- it's-- it's coming from a small place, very warm and caring and-- and familiar, to a big, large, strange.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so that was a tremendous, tremendous adjustment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what helped me was, of course, was I got a job right away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "About, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A few weeks after I came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got a job in Stephen S.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Wise Temple.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's a reform temple in Mulholland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I started teaching Hebrew in Stephen Wise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then about a year later, I got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had my-- my firstborn, Ron. 1971.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I stopped working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was stay at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Being a homemaker for 10 years, and a mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then my younger one was born 1976.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name is Mark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when Mark was about three years old, I went back to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to teach part-time in Temple Judea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I worked there for 10 years, teaching Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that definitely contributed to all kinds of fears that I have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] I'm always terrified of being alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the abandonment is big fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'll do anything just not to be alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I don't know how else-- I'm sure it affected me in many ways that I don't even know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the way-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I definitely wanted to be more for my kids, and I had my mother at home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I certainly don't blame my mother, you know, because I know that these were years of struggle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just-- they needed both to work, and it was just-- she did what you could, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And but she was a career woman, and it required a lot of time from her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wanted to spend more time with my kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
